ghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用不推文"},{"pid":"6a4a55cf34eba884ce79378f8d871f06a330ade3","tid":1780880,"uid":229397,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"dd5b82c1ddf8e6f9b1e3af3ce081637f759c868a","tid":1780880,"uid":162533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"打份工啫做人世咩。同事唔好/難啃好難做落去喎,當你朝9晚6唔OT扣番Lunch1日要對成8粒鐘喎?除非呢份工好好Pay或者比出同面同工種高好多就話啫。放工/Lunch/Break既時間去揾第2份,岩就見,請假都要去見,反正做得2個禮拜,隨時可以byebye佢。做超過1個月就7日通知,過3個月或過Probation就要捱多1個月架喇,你都話呢間野人事差,自己想像下當佢地知道你離職而又要焗住捱1個月先走得會有幾爽?"},{"pid":"06f74b2bf924ca3f656803e98bf3c79265f4e64f","tid":1780880,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"轉工"},{"pid":"0272feb9ea62a0ed9b045c66eba74b94e3f9642b","tid":1780880,"uid":124400,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"你講既問題，九成工都會發生，差別在於幾時發生"},{"pid":"8a6a21cd337f8bf3f3570ef38beda7679435de53","tid":1780880,"uid":162533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0272feb9ea62a0ed9b045c66eba74b94e3f9642b","tid":1780880,"uid":124400,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"你講既問題，九成工都會發生，差別在於幾時發生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T19:37:02.000Z","msg":"所以就擔心可能轉過份工又係咁"},{"pid":"7fabf2a86b85ab740956eae8553a5cb1b2196387","tid":1780880,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"8a6a21cd337f8bf3f3570ef38beda7679435de53","tid":1780880,"uid":162533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0272feb9ea62a0ed9b045c66eba74b94e3f9642b","tid":1780880,"uid":124400,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"你講既問題，九成工都會發生，差別在於幾時發生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T19:37:02.000Z","msg":"所以就擔心可能轉過份工又係咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"既然去到邊都有可能發生，呢度待遇又唔差，不如選擇